## Setup da tabela (Supabase)
Tabela sugerida: `public.contacts`
```sql
create table if not exists public.contacts (
  id bigserial primary key,
  nome_contato text not null,
  phone_1 text,
  phone_2 text,
  phone_3 text,
  created_at timestamptz not null default now()
);